# 栅格化

UI组件库的基石

整个css布局的核心知识

```css
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>栅格化</title>
    <style>
        .row {
            display: flex;
            height: 400px;
            /*width: 400px;*/
            background-color: darkgrey;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .col {
            height: 100%;
        }

        .column-4 {
            background-color: pink;
            flex-basis: calc(40%*0.8);
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .column-6 {
            margin-right: calc(3%);
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: cadetblue;
            flex-basis: calc(60%*0.8);
            display: grid;
            grid-template-rows: repeat(auto-fit,100px);
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,150px);
            justify-content: center;
            align-content: center;
            row-gap: 10px;
            column-gap: 10px;
        }

        .column-6 .sub{
background-color: coral;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col column-6">
        <div class="sub">1</div>
        <div class="sub">2</div>
        <div class="sub">3</div>
        <div class="sub">4</div>
    </div>

    <div class="col column-4"></div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
```



